Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}莉莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}是吗，原来是这样啊，Lilin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}谢谢你，真嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我一直希望你能来阻止二号机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:21:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}若不然，我可能要跟她一起继续活下去
