Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}也跟绫波很像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.26,0:23:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}活下来的应该是熏才对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.43,0:23:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}他比我这种人不知道好多少倍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.61,0:23:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}应该是熏活下来才对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.45,0:23:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不对
